{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b1",
      "translation": "In the fourth quarter of 2020, we celebrated AIA's tenth anniversary of listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Looking back, AIA's listing set multiple records and remains"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b3",
      "translation": "a business that has continued to develop and expand, becoming the world's largest life insurance company by market capitalization."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b5",
      "translation": "All non-executive directors are independent individuals with extensive governance and leadership experience in both public and private sectors. We are committed"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b6",
      "translation": "to maintaining a corporate culture adhering to the highest international governance standards. We firmly believe that deeply rooted governance culture, combined with sound risk"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b7",
      "translation": "management frameworks, form the foundation for sustainable development."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b8",
      "translation": "One of the Board's key responsibilities is ensuring a strong pipeline of leadership talent and implementing effective succession arrangements. We welcomed Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung on 1 June 2020"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b9",
      "translation": "to succeed the retiring Mr. Wong King Fai as Group Chief Executive Officer and President. On behalf of the Board, I express deep appreciation to Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung and his management team"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b10",
      "translation": "for their outstanding management in navigating an unprecedented environment and driving our business forward. We also sincerely thank Mr. Wong King Fai"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b11",
      "translation": "for his excellent leadership and significant contributions to AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b12",
      "translation": "Environmental, social and governance issues are increasingly important globally. We are committed to helping drive society towards a better future, and our environmental,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b14",
      "translation": "demonstrating our excellent corporate governance strength. Additionally, we continued to receive the \"Prime\" Environmental, Social and Governance Corporate Rating from Institutional Shareholder Services"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b18",
      "translation": "Today, customer demand for AIA's products, services and high-quality advice has never been more pressing. Our strategy is built on strong structural growth drivers in Asia,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b20",
      "translation": "digital technology proliferation, and market focus on long-term sustainable development. The Board is confident AIA is well-positioned to capitalize on the significant"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b21",
      "translation": "opportunities in the region, providing financial security to customers and families when needed most, giving them peace of mind, while creating shared value for all stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b24",
      "translation": "Tse Sze Wing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b25",
      "translation": "Independent Non-Executive Chairman"
    }
  ]
}
```
